OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784630877
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in town
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder following an assault in
OL,8,FMaidstone.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to an incident in
OL,11,FReculver Walk at 7:44am on Saturday
OL,12,F(18 July).
OL,14,FIt's alleged a man in his early 50s
OL,15,Fsuffered injuries consistent with stab
OL,16,Fwounds before his white Sprinter van
OL,17,Fwas stolen.
OL,19,FHe was treated by ambulance crews and
OL,20,Fairlifted to a London hospital. The
OL,21,Fman has since been discharged.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
