OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784630877
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in town
OL,6,FPolice discovered a knife in Reculver
OL,7,FWalk and found the victim's van in
OL,8,FWoolley Road.
OL,10,FLater the same morning, a man was
OL,11,Farrested by armed officers in
OL,12,FSwanscombe.
OL,14,FFrancisco Tsumba, 45, of no fixed
OL,15,Faddress, was charged the following day
OL,16,Fwith attempted murder and taking a
OL,17,Fvehicle without consent.
OL,19,FHe appeared at Maidstone Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt on Monday 20 July, where he was
OL,21,Fremanded in custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
