OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784630877
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in town
OL,6,FMr Tsumba is next due to appear at
OL,7,FMaidstone Crown Court on 17 August.
OL,9,FAnyone who witnessed what happened are
OL,10,Fbeing asked to contact Kent Police.
OL,12,FMotorists with dashcam and residents
OL,13,Fwith private CCTV are also urged to
OL,14,Fcheck for relevant footage.
